01:46.497 --> 01:49.400
<i>I ain't taking no trouble</i>

01:49.500 --> 01:54.572
<i>To turn my nights into day</i>

01:54.672 --> 01:56.748
Hello, little Porsche!

02:02.179 --> 02:05.096
Like to go home with me, little Porsche?

02:07.726 --> 02:10.963
Take me all the way to LA
to see my baby!

02:11.062 --> 02:15.559
<i>I can see all the folks,
they're laughin' at me</i>

02:15.942 --> 02:21.281
<i>Cos I'm just naturally crazy</i>

02:21.573 --> 02:23.862
<i>Bad boy</i>

02:29.164 --> 02:33.243
<i>All dressed up in fancy clothes</i>

02:34.668 --> 02:36.875
Jesse! Jesse!

02:39.924 --> 02:44.087
- Jess, take me with you!
- Nah! Risky, baby.

02:45.137 --> 02:48.091
Jess, I ain't scared of nothin'!

03:07.909 --> 03:10.696
Come on, you little baby Porsche!
Come on! Come on!

03:14.958 --> 03:18.493
Yeah, that's right! Yeah!

03:19.879 --> 03:21.160
All right.

03:21.756 --> 03:24.743
So first I go get the money.
Then I go ask Monica.

03:24.843 --> 03:28.591
I say "Monica,
you ever been to Mexico, honey?"

03:32.307 --> 03:36.851
I say "Monica, darlin',
you coming to Mexico with me?"

03:38.647 --> 03:41.634
"Monica, you coming to Mexico with me!"

03:41.734 --> 03:43.344
Me and Monica!

03:43.444 --> 03:45.554
<i>Cos I'm gonna
tell you how it's gonna be!</i>

03:45.654 --> 03:48.026
<i>Mon-Monica and me!</i>

03:48.824 --> 03:52.691
Me and Monica!
Yeah, me and Monica go to Méjico!

03:56.248 --> 03:59.368
Look at that sky!
We got some music here?

04:06.632 --> 04:08.708
Ain't you pretty?

04:10.553 --> 04:12.629
Disco.

04:13.347 --> 04:15.424
Manilow.

04:16.601 --> 04:21.346
I know what we need!
We need the Killer! The Killer rocks on!

04:21.939 --> 04:25.807
Mr Jerry Lee Lewis
and his pumpin' piano!

04:38.121 --> 04:40.941
<i>If you're gonna love me,
lover, please don't tease</i>

04:41.041 --> 04:43.568
<i>If I can hold you, honey, let me squeeze</i>

04:43.668 --> 04:46.488
<i>Well, my heart, it goes round and round</i>

04:46.588 --> 04:48.740
<i>And my love comes tumblin' down</i>

04:48.840 --> 04:54.879
<i>You leave me... ah... breathless!</i>

04:56.306 --> 04:59.876
<i>Oh, I shake all over,
honey, you know why</i>

04:59.976 --> 05:03.391
<i>I'm sure it's love,
baby, now that ain't no lie</i>

05:04.105 --> 05:07.972
Let me have a look here
and see who's lost a Porsche.

05:08.234 --> 05:11.235
Wow! Holy frijoles!

05:12.530 --> 05:14.321
<i>Breathless!</i>

05:15.074 --> 05:16.948
<i>Ooh, baby!</i>

05:17.410 --> 05:19.532
<i>Mmm, crazy!</i>

05:19.745 --> 05:22.273
<i>Honey, you're much too much</i>

05:22.373 --> 05:24.400
<i>Now you know I can't love you enough</i>

05:24.500 --> 05:26.789
<i>It's all right to hold me tight</i>

05:27.086 --> 05:32.506
<i>But when you love me, love me right!</i>

05:33.049 --> 05:35.587
<i>Come on, baby, now you don't be shy</i>

05:35.844 --> 05:38.371
<i>This love was meant for just you and I</i>

05:38.471 --> 05:42.208
<i>Wind, rain, sleet or snow,
I'm gonna get you, baby</i>

05:42.308 --> 05:44.515
My God! Look at that sky!

05:45.103 --> 05:50.097
<i>You leave me... ah... breathless!</i>

05:55.864 --> 05:58.189
Come on, girl! Damn!

05:58.908 --> 06:02.027
Grandma was slow, but she was old!

06:05.998 --> 06:08.489
Hey, girls! You ever kiss a pig?

06:19.595 --> 06:24.007
I say "Monica! I'm comin', baby!
I'm getting closer!"

06:26.143 --> 06:30.506
<i>Baby... baby</i>

06:30.606 --> 06:32.681
<i>Honey, you're much too much</i>

