Jinxed! I swear to God, I am jinxed!

06:43.159 --> 06:46.229
<i>Come on, baby, now you don't be shy</i>

06:46.329 --> 06:48.731
<i>This love was meant for just you and I</i>

06:48.831 --> 06:51.276
<i>Wind, rain, sleet or snow</i>

06:51.376 --> 06:54.070
<i>Honey, Jerry's gonna get you
wherever you go</i>

06:54.170 --> 06:59.591
<i>You... leave me... ah...</i>

07:02.135 --> 07:05.053
<i>Breathless!</i>

07:11.395 --> 07:13.088
Come on!

07:13.188 --> 07:16.308
Goddamn! Piece-of-shit Porsche!

07:24.991 --> 07:26.518
Freeze!

07:26.618 --> 07:30.746
Move away from the car! Let me see
your hands! Get away from the car!

07:31.123 --> 07:34.984
Move! I said move!
Get away from the car, you son of a bitch!

07:35.084 --> 07:37.919
Get away from the car
or I'll blow you away!

08:41.273 --> 08:43.349
Jinxed.

08:53.369 --> 08:56.654
That's right. Keep goin'. Keep goin'.

08:58.207 --> 09:00.662
Around the corner. Nobody home.

09:08.091 --> 09:10.379
Baby, I like yellow.

09:15.723 --> 09:18.131
Monica - 19.

09:22.313 --> 09:24.389
Nobody home.

09:26.401 --> 09:27.802
What do you think?

09:27.902 --> 09:29.978
Hey, good idea.

09:30.863 --> 09:32.556
- Hello?
- Who is it?

09:32.656 --> 09:35.559
- Roto-Rooter.
- Hello?

09:35.659 --> 09:39.953
- Who is there, please?
- Is the pool man. I forgot my key.

10:37.052 --> 10:39.128
Monica!

10:44.017 --> 10:49.438
I'm a bear for ya, baby!
I'm sniffin' around your honey tree!

10:56.738 --> 10:58.974
Monica.

10:59.074 --> 11:01.150
You Frenchy!

11:02.785 --> 11:04.861
Who are you, dopey?

11:06.872 --> 11:08.948
Schmuck!

11:11.377 --> 11:13.499
Back to Disneyland for you.

11:16.173 --> 11:18.047
You're so pretty.

11:38.611 --> 11:41.889
<i>Ah, honey, honey, honey,
hold on real tight</i>

11:41.989 --> 11:44.684
<i>And if you love me, love me right</i>

11:44.784 --> 11:49.779
<i>And if you love me, love me right!</i>

11:52.041 --> 11:54.944
<i>Come on, baby, now don't be shy</i>

11:55.044 --> 11:57.535
<i>Cos love was meant for you and I</i>

12:03.844 --> 12:05.717
Cheese!

12:07.222 --> 12:10.125
Hey, Tolmatchoff. Shake it up!

12:10.225 --> 12:13.012
Not there? Do you know where he is?

12:13.770 --> 12:17.507
Yeah. Yeah, it's Jesse.
I just got back into town.

12:17.607 --> 12:21.345
He's holdin' some money for me.
Gotta have it right away.

12:21.445 --> 12:23.936
Hey, babe, come on. Talk to me.

12:26.992 --> 12:29.483
Right. Catch him at work.

12:36.667 --> 12:38.743
Where are you?

12:40.838 --> 12:43.329
Monica.

12:44.175 --> 12:46.713
<i>Don't know much about history</i>

12:47.887 --> 12:50.923
<i>Don't know much biology</i>

12:52.016 --> 12:54.961
- Who's in there now?
- Monica, the French girl.

12:55.061 --> 12:59.548
- They're squashing her now!
- Those guys are like vampires!

12:59.648 --> 13:01.723
They're flunking everybody!

13:02.817 --> 13:05.345
<i>And I know that if you love me, too</i>

13:05.445 --> 13:09.443
<i>What a wonderful world this would be</i>

13:10.158 --> 13:12.863
<i>Don't know much about geography</i>

13:13.912 --> 13:16.829
<i>Don't know much trigonometry</i>

13:17.540 --> 13:20.375
<i>Don't know much about algebra</i>

13:21.336 --> 13:24.171
<i>Don't know what a slide rule is for</i>

13:25.131 --> 13:28.002
<i>But I do know one and one is two</i>

13:28.927 --> 13:31.464
<i>And if this one could be with you</i>

13:32.763 --> 13:35.207
Let me help you with that.

13:35.307 --> 13:37.751
- Sorry.
- That's OK. You're doing great.

13:37.851 --> 13:40.425
Just keep it cute.

13:42.856 --> 13:45.015
Go on, please.

13:47.152 --> 13:50.764
<i>I can win your love for me</i>

13:50.864 --> 13:54.031
<i>Don't know much about history</i>

13:56.245 --> 13:59.982
There's a review in progress.
You can't go in there now.

14:00.082 --> 14:02.239
Hold that for me.

14:03.292 --> 14:06.827
- Hello, sunshine!
- There's an exam going on in here!

14:08.172 --> 14:10.544
Who is this guy? Do you know him?

14:11.092 --> 14:14.710
Fear not. The Silver Surfer
serves those in distress.

14:17.682 --> 14:21.586
- Is this a friend of yours, Monica?
- Oh, no, no. She don't know me.

14:21.686 --> 14:25.185
I'm here from Maintenance.
They sent me to pick up this table.

14:26.816 --> 14:29.936
Are you crazy?
There's an exam going on in here!

14:31.695 --> 14:36.357
- Go ahead. Ask me a question.
- About how long you gonna be, pal?

14:37.242 --> 14:39.686
I gotta get this
down to art class real quick.

14:39.786 --> 14:43.774
They need something to put
a banana on, so they can draw it.

14:43.874 --> 14:47.444
You can't just draw a banana
when it's lying on the floor.

14:47.544 --> 14:50.656
- Now, just a minute!
- What's going on here?

14:50.756 --> 14:53.492
That's a terrible stain.

14:53.592 --> 14:56.745
Somebody ought to call Security
on that young man!

14:56.845 --> 15:00.843
Hey, look at this. Hey, wild man!

15:04.143 --> 15:07.393
The kid's a good sport. Give her an A.

15:08.105 --> 15:11.854
- Can you go on, Monica?
- You sure you're OK?

15:28.709 --> 15:31.579
<i>Don't know much about history</i>

15:32.545 --> 15:35.297
<i>Don't know much biology</i>

15:36.132 --> 15:38.919
<i>Don't know much about a science book</i>

15:39.677 --> 15:42.844
<i>Don't know much
about the French I took</i>

15:43.306 --> 15:46.224
<i>But I do know that I love you</i>

15:47.143 --> 15:49.963
<i>And I know that if you love me, too</i>

15:50.063 --> 15:53.479
<i>What a wonderful world this would be</i>

15:59.989 --> 16:02.396
Hello, kid!

16:03.158 --> 16:05.436
Do you want to go to Méjico with me?

16:05.536 --> 16:08.439
Did you do this because I left
in the middle of the night?

16:08.539 --> 16:13.117
Did I hurt your feelings
because I didn't say goodbye?

16:15.045 --> 16:17.536
You could have cost me my degree!

16:22.803 --> 16:27.374
All right, all right, all right, all right!
I know I'm crazy. I can't help it.

16:27.474 --> 16:29.627
I guess I love you.

16:29.727 --> 16:34.005
Love? We spent one or two nights
together in Las Vegas, that's all.

16:34.105 --> 16:37.967
- Four. Come on. Let's go to Mexico!
- Don't be ridiculous!

16:38.067 --> 16:41.346
- I have to study.
- All right. Bring your books along.

16:41.446 --> 16:44.098
We'll feed 'em to the big turtles!

16:44.198 --> 16:46.274
But I can't, Jesse.

16:47.368 --> 16:51.580
I have to stay in school or my family
won't send me any more money.

16:52.248 --> 16:57.820
Need money? That's what I'm doin' here.
I'm pickin' up a big bag of money!

16:57.920 --> 17:00.531
But you told me
you had lots of enemies in LA.

17:00.631 --> 17:03.964
Yeah, I do, I do! My enemies and you.

17:05.051 --> 17:08.372
- So you're in danger.
- Yeah, I'm a desperado.

17:08.472 --> 17:10.958
Desperado? What does it mean?

17:11.058 --> 17:14.426
It means I'm desperate for you, Monica!

17:15.645 --> 17:21.510
It's like blasting along the highway,
going 90, maybe 100 miles an hour.

17:21.609 --> 17:24.721
Suddenly there's a dip in the road,
to suck your guts out!

17:24.820 --> 17:27.109
Your breath is gone!

17:28.200 --> 17:31.269
That's me around you, sugar! That's me!

17:31.369 --> 17:33.361
Breathless!

17:34.955 --> 17:37.031
You scare me, Jesse.

17:42.546 --> 17:47.754
You can't just burst into a person's life
and explode it all up like this.

17:49.678 --> 17:53.416
Las Vegas was a holiday.
This is my life!

17:53.516 --> 17:56.635
- Come here!
- Oh, no! Go away, Jesse!

18:02.357 --> 18:07.398
You're wrong, you know! Las Vegas
was real life. This here's a holiday.

18:08.488 --> 18:10.777
Then go back to Las Vegas!

18:22.877 --> 18:27.949
A highway patrolman is on the critical list
at Mercy Hospital, Barstow,

18:28.049 --> 18:30.785
after a shoot-out in the Mojave Desert.

18:30.885 --> 18:34.830
He was found early this morning near
a car stolen in Las Vegas yesterday.

18:34.930 --> 18:37.958
The assailant is believed
to be heading for Los Angeles.

18:38.058 --> 18:42.004
A jacket with a wad of money
but no billfold was left at the scene.

18:42.104 --> 18:45.437
- Here we go.

18:48.652 --> 18:52.264
This is where you wanted
to get out, isn't it?

18:52.364 --> 18:55.034
- Here?
- Oh, yeah. Right. Thanks.

18:55.951 --> 18:57.860
- Thanks a lot.
- OK.

19:04.500 --> 19:08.000
Hello, little honey! Tolmatchoff around?

19:09.088 --> 19:11.164
Thank you.

19:14.177 --> 19:16.253
Hey, kemo sabe!

19:17.221 --> 19:19.712
How ya doin'? Hello, kid.

19:20.683 --> 19:22.557
Hey, sheik.

19:23.144 --> 19:27.853
- Got my money?
- He dropped it off yesterday. Back here.

19:29.192 --> 19:32.052
So what's happening
at the kasbah this week?

19:32.152 --> 19:35.222
- I don't know. How's Vegas?
- Great! I met a little girl.

19:35.322 --> 19:39.106
- We're going to Mexico together.
- So you're on the lam again.

19:39.409 --> 19:41.900
Here you go. Payday.

19:44.039 --> 19:48.819
Said to tell you it was a slick job.
He's ready to go again any time you want.

19:48.919 --> 19:51.280
Wait a minute. What is this? Cheque?

19:51.380 --> 19:54.499
This fuckhead,
he couldn't send me some cash?

19:55.300 --> 19:59.162
I don't know, man. I'm just
an innocent bystander. You know that.

19:59.262 --> 20:04.041
- What am I gonna do with a cheque?
- Those guys play it strictly legit.

20:04.141 --> 20:08.337
- Can you cash it for me?
- Not today. All my breadski's tied up.

20:08.437 --> 20:11.299
- What about Berrutti?
- Saw him yesterday in Venice.

20:11.399 --> 20:14.684
He is rolling in cash. Give him a call.

20:15.820 --> 20:20.057
- Tolmatchoff, got the charts?
- Just a second, boss.

20:20.157 --> 20:23.477
So, tell me. Who is this lovely
young thing you came to see?

20:23.577 --> 20:26.365
French girl. Schoolgirl. Great girl.

20:27.540 --> 20:29.817
Kills me!

20:29.917 --> 20:32.407
Yeah. Is Berrutti there?

20:34.713 --> 20:37.204
What time's he gonna be back?

20:39.092 --> 20:42.245
Well, look, tell him... Tell him that...

20:42.345 --> 20:45.582
Tell him Jesse's looking for him.
I'll call back later.

20:45.682 --> 20:46.713
Bye.

20:50.520 --> 20:54.883
There's something else about her,
you know. Something in her eyes.

20:54.983 --> 20:57.344
French, you know?

20:57.444 --> 21:00.813
- God! You're such a fuck-up!
- Yeah, I know.

21:02.531 --> 21:04.689
Adiós, amigo.

21:31.559 --> 21:34.337
Tolmatchoff!
I told you I smelled something!

21:34.437 --> 21:37.048
- Hello, Lieutenant.
- Enright and me were reminiscing.

21:37.148 --> 21:40.343
Remember when you turned in
your buddy Johnny Goddard?

21:40.443 --> 21:43.304
- You guys needed some help.
- It's gonna happen again.

21:43.404 --> 21:47.934
Jesse Lujack? Also known as Jesse
Lee Burns. Also known as Jack Burns.

21:48.034 --> 21:52.105
Five ten, 160 pounds. Age 28.
Medium-length brown hair.

21:52.205 --> 21:56.651
This dump is his last known
place of work. Street punk.

21:56.751 --> 22:01.530
So what? I know him. He worked here.
Made some deliveries a few years ago.

22:01.630 --> 22:04.533
- So has he been around here lately?
- No.

22:04.633 --> 22:07.828
Lieutenant, this person
you're looking for.

22:07.928 --> 22:11.415
- Is he kind of a seedy Vegas boy?
- Yeah, maybe.

22:11.515 --> 22:15.460
Thinks he's cute.
Somebody like that just left.

22:15.560 --> 22:17.629
Bingo!

22:17.729 --> 22:21.430
Accessory to murder!
You know what that means!

23:15.577 --> 23:18.396
Hey, kid. Take those home
and put 'em on your boots.

23:18.496 --> 23:20.572
Hey, wow! Thanks!

25:27.413 --> 25:31.326
Anaheim, San Diego,
Tijuana, points south!

25:34.794 --> 25:37.864
Didn't you have
a different car in Las Vegas?

25:37.964 --> 25:43.006
Yeah. That one's in the shop getting fixed.
This one's just a loaner.

25:48.975 --> 25:51.300
Good wind, huh?

25:52.103 --> 25:54.262
It's so hot. You like it?

25:55.273 --> 25:57.884
Yeah. The hotter the better.

25:57.984 --> 26:02.978
Gotta love those Santa Anas, honey!
Just stokin' up the fires!

26:06.700 --> 26:08.859
Where you goin'?

26:09.912 --> 26:12.284
Downtown. Bonaventure Hotel.

26:13.540 --> 26:16.485
Come on, get in. I know a short cut.

26:16.585 --> 26:18.743
Come on.

26:21.674 --> 26:23.750
Come on.

26:32.308 --> 26:35.926
<i>Open up, honey,
it's your lover-boy me that's a-knockin'</i>

26:36.896 --> 26:41.439
<i>Why don't you listen to me, sugar?
All the cats are at the high school rockin'</i>

26:41.943 --> 26:44.398
<i>Time to get your boppin' shoes</i>

26:44.696 --> 26:48.891
- You know who that is, don't you?
- Yeah. You told me in Vegas.

26:48.991 --> 26:51.696
Another crazy man. Lee Lewis?

26:52.078 --> 26:54.981
Another crazy man? Another crazy man?

26:55.081 --> 27:00.153
No! This is the one, the only,
the original, the true Jerry Lee Lewis!

27:00.253 --> 27:02.707
Listen to this guy! He means it!

27:04.506 --> 27:07.626
Can't stop, won't stop, never stop! Wow!

27:08.051 --> 27:11.385
Jerry Lee - he's burnin'! B-B-Burnin'!

27:18.478 --> 27:22.061
- What's so funny, honey?
- You! Those clothes!

27:22.858 --> 27:25.761
You don't like 'em? I'll take 'em off!

27:25.861 --> 27:28.233
No! Stop!

27:29.197 --> 27:31.682
What happened to the blue suit
you had in Vegas?

27:31.782 --> 27:34.700
- Blue suit?
- Yeah. Your lucky suit.

27:35.119 --> 27:37.491
It wasn't the suit that was lucky.
It was you.

27:37.663 --> 27:42.040
When you walked out,
I started rolling fool's dice.

27:44.003 --> 27:46.906
Fool's dice. Snake eyes.

27:47.006 --> 27:49.082
Double zero.

27:50.259 --> 27:52.335
You roll dice too much.

27:53.095 --> 27:55.171
You think that, huh?

28:02.312 --> 28:07.104
You think maybe I was rollin' dice
when I should have been rollin' you?

28:07.776 --> 28:09.934
<i>Rockin' at the high school hop</i>

28:10.362 --> 28:12.847
<i>Because they're jumpin'
at the high school hop</i>

28:12.947 --> 28:15.023
<i>We're rollin' at the high school hop</i>

28:17.035 --> 28:19.604
- I gotta make a stop.
- But my appointment!

28:19.704 --> 28:22.741
It's all right.
It'll just take a minute.

28:29.673 --> 28:31.463
What is this place?

